updates.update_content:
Andrew, our game designer, is a structural thinker. Today he started the productions for the Hob Goblin award. Handmade boffer swords that are crafted works of usable art! For more on what one uses a boffer sword for, click here: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Foam_weapon
You may scoff at the fine art of boffer fighting, but Andrew has a great philosophy on the matter; 
"When we can use our adrenaline, and often testosterone, in a healthy manner, it removes anger issues and the need to constantly carry stress in our bodies. It's a way of acting out our primitive nature in a way that is stimulating to mind and body."
